ting experience Associate's degree in accounting or business administration Strong Microsoft Excel skills Strong knowledge of accounting principles Strong math skills Great verbal and written communication skills Bookkeeper related job titles: Accountant Assistant Junior Bookkeeper Senior Bookkeeper Accounting Associate Office Bookkeeper Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
